    {
      "id": "partarticle",
      "icon": "🔗",
      "title": "Particles + the",
      "subtitle": "Partiċelli mal-artiklu — particle contractions",
      "intro": "When a particle meets the article 'l-', they fuse into one word. Example: bi + l → bil-, ġo + l → ġol-.",
      "items": [
        {
          "long": "ma' + l-",
          "short": "mal-",
          "en": "with the"
        },
        {
          "long": "ta' + l-",
          "short": "tal-",
          "en": "of the"
        },
        {
          "long": "sa + l-",
          "short": "sal-",
          "en": "until the / as far as the"
        },
        {
          "long": "ġo + l-",
          "short": "ġol-",
          "en": "in the"
        },
        {
          "long": "bi + l-",
          "short": "bil-",
          "en": "with the"
        },
        {
          "long": "fi + l-",
          "short": "fil-",
          "en": "in the"
        },
        {
          "long": "lil + l-",
          "short": "lill-",
          "en": "to the"
        },
        {
          "long": "bħal + l-",
          "short": "bħall-",
          "en": "like the"
        },
        {
          "long": "għal + l-",
          "short": "għall-",
          "en": "for the"
        },
        {
          "long": "minn + l-",
          "short": "mill-",
          "en": "from the"
        }
      ],
      "facts": [
        "These contractions still follow the sun-consonant rule from Lesson 1.",
        "Before sun consonants (ċ, d, n, r, s, t, x, ż, z), the L assimilates: fil-xemx → fix-xemx; ġol-sodda → ġos-sodda.",
        "Before vowels, h, or għ — the particles bi, fi shorten to b' / f': fi dar → f'dar; bi ajruplan → b'ajruplan.",
        "The particles sa, ma', ta' may also shorten before vowels: sa Għawdex → s'Għawdex; ma' ommi → m'ommi."
      ],
      "exercises": [
        {
          "id": "ex3",
          "title": "Combine particle + article",
          "instructions": "Pick the correct contracted form.",
          "choices": [
            "sal-",
            "bil-",
            "ġol-",
            "lill-",
            "mill-",
            "fil-",
            "mal-",
            "tal-",
            "bħall-",
            "għall-"
          ],
          "items": [
            {
              "sentence": "Oħti ħarġet ___ ġnien",
              "en": "My sister went to the garden",
              "answer": "sal-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Iz-ziju mar dawra ___ kelb",
              "en": "Uncle went on a walk with the dog",
              "answer": "bil-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Jien mort ___ ġnien biex naqra",
              "en": "I went into the garden to read",
              "answer": "ġol-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "___ kuġin inħobbu ħafna",
              "en": "I love the cousin a lot",
              "answer": "lill-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Xtrajt għaġin ___ ħanut",
              "en": "I bought pasta from the shop",
              "answer": "mill-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Dlikt il-ħobż ___ butir",
              "en": "I spread the bread with butter",
              "answer": "bil-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Weħilt ___ lift",
              "en": "I got stuck in the lift",
              "answer": "fil-"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Mort sal-Belt ___ kuġina",
              "en": "I went to Valletta with the cousin",
              "answer": "mal-"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
